                <li>
                    <span class="icon24 icomoon-icon-arrow-down-2 red"></span><span style="font-size:13px; color:orange;font-weight:bold;">@ViewBag.sp3</span> : @ViewBag.phantram3 % Lượt mua <span class="pull-right strong">@ViewBag.count3</span>
